reviews.review_text:
Drums Drums is pretty interesting, a long intro gives way to some electro drums or whatever you wanna call it and then at around 11mins into it gets weird and trippy. Never really was into Drums/Space but this gets me wanting to check out some more. 

Show is decent but not great, Crazy fingers is a highlight
